Major cleanup + orbital backflow implementation + experiment report

Cleanup:
- Remove ~45 dead run scripts, dead notebooks, dead function modules
- Remove all old model checkpoints (~261MB)
- Remove dead result directories (logs, csvs, eigenstate_sweep, etc.)
- Update .gitignore (ignore *.pt, results/arch_colloc/*.log)

New features:
- OrbitalBackflowNet: copresheaf GNN for orbital matrix perturbation
- Multiplicative orbital backflow with scheduled bf_scale ramp
- Training, evaluation, and architecture comparison scripts
- jastrow_architectures.py: CTNNJastrowVCycle and variants

Key results (N=6, w=1.0, E_DMC=20.15932):
- Jastrow only (V-cycle): E=20.188 (+0.14%)
- + MLP coord backflow:   E=20.179 (+0.10%)
- + CTNN coord backflow:  E=20.173 (+0.07%)
- + Orbital BF (mult):    E=20.189 (probe, ep100, still training)
